@startuml

title Marketplace Admin Report Listing and Filtering Sequence Diagram

actor "Marketplace Admin" as Admin

participant "Frontend (Website)" as FE
participant "Apache\n(HTTP Server)" as Apache

box "Laravel Application" #LightGreen
  participant "Middleware" as MW
  participant "UserReportController" as URC
  participant "Eloquent ORM" as ORM
end box

database "MariaDB Database" as DB

note right of Admin
Marketplace Admin reviews marketplace
reports, filters them, and selects
moderation actions from the reports table.
end note

note left of DB
It is assumed the Marketplace Admin is
authenticated/authorized unless an exception occurs.
end note


== Open Marketplace Management Page ==

Admin -> FE: Open market management page
activate Admin
activate FE
activate Apache
activate MW
activate URC
activate ORM
activate DB

FE -> Apache: GET /marketplace_management

alt Route exists
    Apache -> MW: Forward HTTP marketplace management request
else Route not found
    Apache --> FE: 404 Not Found
    FE --> Admin: Display "Marketplace management route not found" error
end

alt Valid + Authorized
    MW -> URC: Pass authenticated and authorized marketplace management request
else Validation/Auth error
    MW --> FE: 401 Unauthorized / 403 Forbidden
    FE --> Admin: Display validation or authorization error
end

URC -> ORM: Load initial marketplace reports with reporter and reported user relationships
ORM -> DB: SELECT reports with related reporter and reported_user data

alt Initial report query success
    DB --> ORM: Marketplace report result set
    ORM --> URC: reports collection
    URC --> FE: Return marketplace_management view
    FE --> Admin: Display report table and management actions
else Initial report query failure
    DB --> ORM: Query failed / SQL exception
    ORM --> URC: Marketplace report retrieval failed
    URC --> FE: 500 Internal Server Error
    FE --> Admin: Display system error while loading marketplace reports
end


== Refresh Reports Data ==

FE -> Apache: GET /reports/data

alt Route exists
    Apache -> MW: Forward HTTP reports data request
else Route not found
    Apache --> FE: 404 Not Found
    FE --> Admin: Display "Reports data route not found" error
end

alt Valid + Authorized
    MW -> URC: Pass authenticated and authorized reports data request
else Validation/Auth error
    MW --> FE: 401 Unauthorized / 403 Forbidden
    FE --> Admin: Display validation or authorization error
end

URC -> ORM: Load reports with reporter, reported user, and related identifiers
ORM -> DB: SELECT reports with reporter, reported_user, post_id, and reported_user_id

alt Reports data query success
    DB --> ORM: Refreshed marketplace report dataset
    ORM --> URC: Report collection retrieved
    URC --> FE: Return reports JSON response
    FE --> Admin: Render reports table rows
else Reports data query failure
    DB --> ORM: Query failed / SQL exception
    ORM --> URC: Reports data retrieval failed
    URC --> FE: 500 Internal Server Error
    FE --> Admin: Display system error while refreshing reports
end


== Filter Reports ==

Admin -> FE: Search by user/seller or filter by reason/date

alt Matching reports found
    FE --> Admin: Display filtered reports and pagination
else No matching reports found
    FE --> Admin: Display "No se encuentran reportes."
end

@enduml